<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.8.8">
<l>kōlamē tāmaraik kaṇṇatō rañcaṉa</l>
<l>nīlamē niṉṟeṉa tāviyai yīrkiṉṟa</l>
<l>cīlamē ceṉṟucel lātaṉa muṉṉilāṅ</l>
<l>kālamē yuṉṉaiyen nāḷkaṇṭu koḷvaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O the beauty of the lotus eyes, o the unique kajal</l>
<l>colour, o the nature that stands [and] cuts my</l>
<l>soul, o the times that have gone, not gone [and] stand</l> 
<l>before [me] – which day shall I see you for myself?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
